    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SeaBed是一部广受好评的精神悬疑小说，以3个女孩的视角来讲述的百合悬疑故事。水野佐知子：设计师。她总是见到过去恋人的幻觉。楢崎响：佐知子的朋友兼精神科医生。她在研究着人类记忆的运作方式。贵呼：佐知子的儿时玩伴兼前恋人。她有发作性记忆障碍，也不记得自己是怎样和佐知子离别的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她们生活在不同的世界，却追求着同样的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了将幻想与真实分隔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了找到自己活着的意义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/015003fd04bcf7b9590043d2907f5bbf.poster.avif?t=1732731242\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/015003fd04bcf7b9590043d2907f5bbf.webm?t=1732731242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/015003fd04bcf7b9590043d2907f5bbf.mp4?t=1732731242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“有时，我会在夜里醒来，感觉身边的声音似乎放大了无数倍，脑袋也疼得要命。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水野佐知子大学毕业后为了找工作直接搬到东京，但很快她就辞职了，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与儿时玩伴的贵呼一起创立了四叶草设计公司，并担任社长一职。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她的主要爱好是阅读，不过其实她只是对其它事情都不感兴趣而已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学生时代的她经常读书，而工作后只要有时间也会读书。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自从在儿时遇到了与自己截然不同，总是充满活力的贵呼后，就开始对她的一言一行产生了兴趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/31e5fc6cb8c0d06cab528b5dc7b1033c.poster.avif?t=1732731242\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/31e5fc6cb8c0d06cab528b5dc7b1033c.webm?t=1732731242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/31e5fc6cb8c0d06cab528b5dc7b1033c.mp4?t=1732731242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“难得有机会，我也想看看呀。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贵呼是个对什么事情都非常感兴趣的女生，周围的人总觉得她是个长不大的孩子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对小时候遇到的同性的佐知子一见钟情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要说是同性恋的话，又似乎有所不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她自己主张说只是佐知子恰巧是女生罢了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被后天性记忆障碍所困扰。无法想起很多事情，对此她总觉得很遗憾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/a705dee16d5e9950c7a2969ddf85069f.poster.avif?t=1732731242\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/a705dee16d5e9950c7a2969ddf85069f.webm?t=1732731242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/a705dee16d5e9950c7a2969ddf85069f.mp4?t=1732731242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我只是喜欢观察人们。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >楢崎响她经营着一家名为楢崎心理诊所的精神科诊所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她和佐知子是同乡，自小关系甚密，然而初中以后两人就开始疏远了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她知道佐知子受幻觉症状所困扰的时候，就开始为她诊治。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许是因为她经常思考事情，她总是对喝咖啡的事情很讲究。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然她不信仰宗教，但却相信着“一切事物都有其存在的意义，只要时机成熟自会发挥其作用。”这样的说法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/583090/extras/b0ea9de494803da3b8e6a6a020903117.avif?t=1732731242\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
